Paper: hep-th/0110244

Date: 2001-10-26

Title: Boundary Liouville Field Theory

Authors: B.Ponsot, J.Teschner

Comments: 18 pages

Journal-ref: Nucl.Phys. B622 (2002) 309-327

Liouville field theory is considered on domains with conformally invariantboundary conditions. We present an explicit expression for the three pointfunction of boundary fields in terms of the fusion coefficients which determinethe monodromy properties of the conformal blocks.